text: Frank Lasky (born October 4, 1941) is a former American football tackle. He played for the New York Giants from 1964 to 1965. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:American football tackles Category:Florida Gators football players Category:New York Giants players Category:Montreal Alouettes players Category:Players of American football from New York (state)
